 <title>&kw-hos-tm; 5.0: Block Storage Service (Cinder) Features</title>
 <para>
  Block Storage Service (Cinder) implements services and libraries to provide
  on-demand, self-service access to Block Storage resources via abstraction and
  automation on top of other block storage devices.
 </para>
